title: I cant find the second loot item :( I misclicked home..
body: In the pic I unlocked two items.. when I went to go click to league i misclicked the home button.. now I cant find what my second item was its like it disappeared or got cancelled. i cant find any new skins, emotes, icons or wards.

replies.body: What did you open to get the rewards? A revel orb? Do you have an extra gemstone or golden token?
